    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Setting up Octopress with Org-Mode]]></title>
    <link href="http://ronert-obst.com/blog/2013-05-17-setting-up-octopress-with-org-mode.html"/>
    <updated>2013-05-17T11:36:00+02:00</updated>
